Package: libglesv2-vivante1
Section: libs
Architecture: arm64
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libgal-vivante1 (=6.2.4.p4.0-1), libvsc-vivante1 (=6.2.4.p4.0-1), libc6
Conflicts: libgles2
Replaces: libgles2
Provides: libgles2
Description: Vivante implementation of the OpenGL|ES 2.x API -- development files
 OpenGL|ES is a cross-platform API for full-function 2D and 3D graphics on
 embedded systems - including consoles, phones, appliances and vehicles.
 It contains a subset of OpenGL plus a number of extensions for the
 special needs of embedded systems.
 .
 OpenGL|ES 2.x provides an API for programmable hardware including vertex
 and fragment shaders.

Package: libglesv2-vivante1-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libglesv2-vivante1 (=6.2.4.p4.0-1)
Multi-Arch: same
Description: Vivante implementation of the OpenGL|ES 2.x API -- development files
 OpenGL|ES is a cross-platform API for full-function 2D and 3D graphics on
 embedded systems - including consoles, phones, appliances and vehicles.
 It contains a subset of OpenGL plus a number of extensions for the
 special needs of embedded systems.
 .
 OpenGL|ES 2.x provides an API for programmable hardware including vertex
 and fragment shaders.
 .
 This package provides a development environment for building applications
 using the OpenGL|ES 2.x APIs.


